oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Wells, Kitty;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3197) for an order placed by Consolidated Enterprises for 100 two color window cards for a performance by Kitty Wells and Johnny Wright at the East Campus High School Gym in Waukegan, Wisconsin on October 27. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
